    "description": "<strong>《骨哥开冲》</strong>是一款快节奏动作游戏，你将扮演一个隐藏在骷髅之下的神秘竞速战士，追回自己被盗的领土，并机智处理大量爆炸物！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >快速反应，勇往直前！</h2><br>迷宫，机关，还有大量的爆炸挡在面前，而骷髅战士只能凭借着无与伦比的灵活性躲避危险，而你的任务只有一个，那就是向前！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2197360/extras/59e81f86a8a38d9c1ef88a3d074f0633.poster.avif?t=1756492247\" width=720 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2197360/extras/59e81f86a8a38d9c1ef88a3d074f0633.webm?t=1756492247\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2197360/extras/59e81f86a8a38d9c1ef88a3d074f0633.mp4?t=1756492247\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >多名角色，智取迷宫！</h2><br>除了可爱的骷髅战士外，随着流程的推进你还可以解锁其他四名角色，他们造型各异，能力不一。想象一下，如果你操控的是一台会四处发射炮弹的暴躁显示器……<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2197360/extras/876066f387c6d48d28895a8b9c151720.poster.avif?t=1756492247\" width=720 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2197360/extras/876066f387c6d48d28895a8b9c151720.webm?t=1756492247\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2197360/extras/876066f387c6d48d28895a8b9c151720.mp4?t=1756492247\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >烧脑关卡，谁可一战？</h2><br>既然是迷宫动作游戏，那么迷宫不够烧脑怎么行呢？游戏里有着大量画风各异，创意十足的迷宫关卡，玩家每到达新的关卡，都会迎接全新的挑战！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2197360/extras/8dfb534c4e780d9de2617fe21632a862.poster.avif?t=1756492247\" width=720 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2197360/extras/8dfb534c4e780d9de2617fe21632a862.webm?t=1756492247\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2197360/extras/8dfb534c4e780d9de2617fe21632a862.mp4?t=1756492247\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>最后请记住，骨哥开冲，好玩到“爆炸”！</strong>",
